Package ca.cgjennings.ui

Interface NestingDocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Document
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AutocompletionDocument
    public interface NestingDocument
extends Document
    This interface should be implemented by Documents that wrap around other documents to modify their basic functionality. (Such wrapping can be used to simulate the effects of multiple inheritence.) The interface specifies a getDocument method that allows nesting-aware code to access the document(s) being wrapped.
    Author:
    Chris Jennings
